1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Cinta Di Luar Kubur=
(Diadaptasi daripada novel oleh Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episod 6=

3
00:01:46,550 --> 00:01:47,580
- Bunuh dia!
- Bunuh dia!

4
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:48,910
Kamu sekalian

5
00:01:48,910 --> 00:01:50,750
tinggi dan perkasa.

6
00:01:51,420 --> 00:01:52,910
Awak mahu saya mati?

7
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:55,060
Jika saya terpaksa mati,

8
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:57,270
kita akan mati bersama!

9
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:29,550
(Jika anda mati dengan obsesi jahat,)

10
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:32,460
(roh jahat akan datang
dan melanda dunia.)

11
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:35,390
Siapakah gadis ini?

12
00:02:35,510 --> 00:02:36,350
Saya tidak tahu.

13
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:01,540
Saya...

14
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:09,020
Pekan saya, Liangzhou,

15
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:10,830
telah dimusnahkan oleh tentera Chong.

16
00:03:12,350 --> 00:03:13,350
Rakan senegara saya

17
00:03:13,350 --> 00:03:14,420
dibunuh oleh mereka.

18
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:17,390
Tadi, saya mendengar kata-kata liarnya,

19
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:18,950
dan kemarahan menyelubungi saya.

20
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:22,460
Jadi, saya bermati-matian untuk membunuhnya.

21
00:03:24,270 --> 00:03:25,110
Saya...

22
00:03:39,140 --> 00:03:40,580
Jangan tarik pedang saya sambil lewa.

23
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:45,460
Tolong jangan salahkan saya, Jeneral.

24
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:52,990
Anda banyak menyumbang kepada tentera saya.

25
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:55,390
Kesedihan menguasai kamu,

26
00:03:55,390 --> 00:03:56,230
dan kamu membunuhnya.

27
00:03:57,580 --> 00:03:58,700
Saya tidak akan menyalahkan awak.

28
00:03:59,270 --> 00:04:00,950
Bravo! Syabas!

29
00:04:00,950 --> 00:04:07,070
- Syabas!
- Awak berjaya!

30
00:04:12,180 --> 00:04:13,020
Cik He,

31
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:14,550
dia tidak mengaku

32
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:15,900
bagaimana dia menyelinap ke dalam jelapang.

33
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:16,740
Awak...

34
00:04:16,740 --> 00:04:17,990
Bagaimana awak boleh bunuh dia?

35
00:04:19,150 --> 00:04:19,990
Encik Lin,

36
00:04:21,350 --> 00:04:22,550
kami masih boleh menyoal siasat

37
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:23,390
pengawal yang bertugas.

38
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:24,860
Tidak terlalu banyak yang terbakar.

39
00:04:25,350 --> 00:04:26,190
Tidak mengapa.

40
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:28,940
Padamkan segera,

41
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:30,260
api tidak banyak marak.

42
00:04:30,930 --> 00:04:31,770
Itu bagus!

43
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:32,940
Semua orang, jangan panik.

44
00:04:34,300 --> 00:04:35,940
Nanti kami agihkan makanan.

45
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:37,150
Edarkan makanan?

46
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,150
Jadi, kami benar-benar tidak

47
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,300
rugi terlalu banyak.

48
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,420
Semua orang, bersurai.

49
00:04:42,030 --> 00:04:42,910
Bergerak, semua orang.

50
00:04:42,910 --> 00:04:43,990
Semua orang, pulang.

51
00:04:43,990 --> 00:04:44,940
Putuskan.

52
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:46,140
Jangan risau.

53
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,470
Kami akan mengagihkan makanan

54
00:04:47,470 --> 00:04:48,420
mengikut jadual.

55
00:04:49,670 --> 00:04:50,740
- Pulang ke rumah.
- Pergi.

56
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:51,700
Putuskan.

57
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:56,790
Mengapa kamu berbuat demikian?

58
00:05:00,030 --> 00:05:01,420
Jika He Yan mati seperti itu,

59
00:05:01,670 --> 00:05:02,740
roh jahat akan menjadi mangsa.

60
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,380
Berpura-puralah saya usil.

61
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:10,630
Jeneral Duan,

62
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,300
bagaimana di bumi

63
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:15,820
anda mendapat pedang ini?

64
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:18,260
Itu cerita yang panjang.

65
00:05:19,350 --> 00:05:20,790
Pada suatu hari, di jambatan Nandu,

66
00:05:21,550 --> 00:05:22,590
saya bertemu seorang lelaki tua.

67
00:05:25,710 --> 00:05:26,740
Ini adalah kebenaran.

68
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:28,910
Tidak lama sebelum saya pergi,

69
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:30,420
saya bertemu seorang lelaki tua yang aneh

70
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:31,260
di jambatan itu.

71
00:05:31,790 --> 00:05:33,230
Dia berkata dia berumur ratusan tahun.

72
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:35,380
Dia tiba-tiba menghalang saya

73
00:05:35,790 --> 00:05:36,740
dan memberikan saya pedang ini.

74
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:38,310
Dia juga memberitahu saya

75
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,500
itu adalah Pembebasan.

76
00:05:40,260 --> 00:05:41,420
Ia bermaksud menghilangkan ilusi

77
00:05:42,230 --> 00:05:43,420
dan kebencian manusia.

78
00:05:43,990 --> 00:05:44,990
Mereka yang terkenanya

79
00:05:45,420 --> 00:05:46,500
akan menyingkirkan ilusi.

80
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:50,790
Begitulah awak, Cik He.

81
00:05:52,300 --> 00:05:53,230
Anda tahu segala-galanya.

82
00:06:01,590 --> 00:06:02,430
Saya akan pergi menyiasat

83
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:03,500
kes kebakaran.

84
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:04,580
Saya akan ambil cuti.

85
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:06,660
Jeneral Duan,

86
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:10,350
anda lihat betapa peliknya saya berkelakuan.

87
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:12,260
Tidakkah anda mengesyaki

88
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:13,350
bahawa saya telah dihantar

89
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:15,060
oleh Duke Pei atau Chong Utara?

90
00:06:15,550 --> 00:06:17,300
Adakah anda hanya menerima pesanan daripada orang?

91
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,350
Berdasarkan tengkorak anda,

92
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:21,500
anda dilahirkan tidak terkawal

93
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:23,740
dan anda bertindak atas kuasa anda sendiri.

94
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:32,460
(Adakah dia)

95
00:06:32,670 --> 00:06:34,230
(mendapat Pembebasan)

96
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:36,150
(kerana dia adalah pembawa mantera saya?)

97
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:43,140
Ada apa?

98
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:44,260
Moyang Besar,

99
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:46,060
Saya jumpa Duan Xu yang sebenar!

100
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,120
Apa khabar?

101
00:06:47,150 --> 00:06:48,260
Saya menjumpai Du Zheng,

102
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,860
yang berkhidmat dengan Duan Xu di Daizhou.

103
00:06:50,150 --> 00:06:51,150
Dia memberi saya potret

104
00:06:51,150 --> 00:06:52,060
tuan muda

105
00:06:52,060 --> 00:06:53,380
yang pernah dihidangkannya.

106
00:06:57,110 --> 00:06:59,500
Fang Xianye, Kaunselor Penapisan.

107
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:02,380
Dia ialah Duan Xu yang sebenar.

108
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:05,980
(Fang Xianye, Penasihat Penapisan)

109
00:07:05,990 --> 00:07:06,830
Tuanku,

110
00:07:07,470 --> 00:07:08,310
tidak ada jalan.

111
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:12,820
Bolehkah kita benar-benar tidak
menghantar bekalan ke Shuozhou

112
00:07:14,030 --> 00:07:16,740
tanpa penderitaan

113
00:07:17,550 --> 00:07:19,790
(Maharaja Besar Liang)
ada kemalangan jiwa?

114
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:23,220
Tuanku.

115
00:07:23,220 --> 00:07:24,150
(Yao Jianhe, Duke Pei)

116
00:07:24,150 --> 00:07:25,820
Walaupun Duan Xu telah menduduki Shuozhou,

117
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:28,300
(Du Yanting, Canselor)
dia mengingkari perintah

118
00:07:28,590 --> 00:07:29,470
dan melanggar undang-undang.

119
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:30,790
(Duan Chengzhang, Menteri Ritus)
Dia menghantar tentera

120
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:31,790
tanpa memberitahu sesiapa.

121
00:07:32,260 --> 00:07:34,550
Jadi tenteranya telah terperangkap

122
00:07:34,910 --> 00:07:35,860
di Shuozhou.

123
00:07:36,150 --> 00:07:36,990
Sekarang,

124
00:07:37,110 --> 00:07:38,420
malah 200,000 askar Hulan

125
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:39,260
mengintai dengan rakus.

126
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:40,470
Bagaimanakah bekalan

127
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:43,300
boleh dihantar ke Shuozhou?

128
00:07:43,740 --> 00:07:45,110
Adakah anda berkata

129
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:47,420
kami akan meninggalkan

130
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:49,380
dua puluh ribu askar

131
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:50,260
dan rakyat?

132
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:51,100
Bagaimanakah kami boleh membantu?

133
00:07:51,790 --> 00:07:53,030
Nyawa Duan Xu penting.

134
00:07:53,620 --> 00:07:55,260
Bagaimana dengan kehidupan

135
00:07:55,260 --> 00:07:56,790
- askar lain?
- Awak...

136
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:57,630
Cukup.

137
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:02,230
Chong Utara telah menduduki
utara Sungai Guanhe

138
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:03,070
selama tiga puluh tahun.

139
00:08:03,590 --> 00:08:05,500
Sekarang, kita akan menyeberangi sungai.

140
00:08:05,710 --> 00:08:07,590
Kita tidak boleh meninggalkan Shuozhou begitu sahaja.

141
00:08:07,910 --> 00:08:08,750
Walau bagaimanapun,

142
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,740
apa yang Jeneral Duan lakukan
amat berbahaya.

143
00:08:10,910 --> 00:08:12,820
Kebimbangan Duke Pei adalah wajar.

144
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:14,900
Tuanku,

145
00:08:15,150 --> 00:08:16,260
Shuozhou sedang dikepung.

146
00:08:16,470 --> 00:08:17,740
Bekalan akan habis.

147
00:08:17,990 --> 00:08:19,230
Walaupun peluang tipis,

148
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:20,670
kami tidak boleh mengalah.

149
00:08:20,910 --> 00:08:22,420
Kami faham Menteri Duan

150
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:23,260
mengambil berat terhadap anaknya.

151
00:08:23,620 --> 00:08:24,460
Tetapi sekarang,

152
00:08:24,590 --> 00:08:25,910
tiada siapa yang dapat melawan jalannya

153
00:08:25,910 --> 00:08:27,300
melalui 200,000 askar Hulan.

154
00:08:27,910 --> 00:08:28,910
Kami boleh mengumpul bekalan

155
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,470
sebelum kami berjaya menyampaikannya.

156
00:08:30,990 --> 00:08:31,830
Siapa yang akan

157
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:33,590
mengambil misi ini?

158
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:37,340
Saya.

159
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:38,310
Saya akan mengambil misi ini.

160
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:43,470
Mahkamah ditolak!

161
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,430
Anda menyuruh anak saya dibuang ke hadapan.

162
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:55,900
Dan sekarang, anda mahu membunuhnya.

163
00:09:05,580 --> 00:09:07,340
(Dewan Chongde)

164
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:08,430
He Yan mendapat kunci

165
00:09:08,430 --> 00:09:09,710
jelapang daripada Xie.

166
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:11,430
Jelas sekali, dia tahu

167
00:09:11,740 --> 00:09:13,710
orang Lin menjaga jelapang bersama kami.

168
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:15,350
Dia juga tahu sangat

169
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:16,990
tentang rondaan dan syif.

170
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:18,430
Kapten Han,

171
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:20,260
anda bertanggungjawab ke atas pertahanan jelapang.

172
00:09:20,830 --> 00:09:21,670
Anda mesti mengetahui

173
00:09:22,190 --> 00:09:23,030
apa yang berlaku hari ini.

174
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:23,910
Ya.

175
00:09:27,310 --> 00:09:28,150
Jeneral Duan.

176
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,330
Jeneral Duan,

177
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:30,500
Saya meminta pertimbangan anda yang adil.

178
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,380
Jeneral Duan!

179
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:32,990
Saya takut ada orang lain

180
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:34,620
di belakang Xie.

181
00:09:35,110 --> 00:09:36,350
Berbanding dengan mencari pengintip,

182
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:38,950
kami mempunyai sesuatu yang lebih mendesak untuk dilakukan.

183
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:43,140
Saya telah menyekat berita.

184
00:09:44,380 --> 00:09:45,470
Tetapi saya ingin berterus terang

185
00:09:45,990 --> 00:09:46,950
dengan anda semua.

186
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:49,230
Bekalan daripada Marshal Qin

187
00:09:49,950 --> 00:09:50,950
sudah cukup

188
00:09:50,950 --> 00:09:51,900
selama lima belas hari.

189
00:09:53,140 --> 00:09:54,710
Tetapi mereka telah dibakar menjadi abu.

190
00:09:55,710 --> 00:09:57,190
Apa yang kita ada sekarang hanyalah makanan

191
00:09:57,380 --> 00:09:58,780
Encik Lin telah kumpulkan untuk saya.

192
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:01,590
Jauh dari cukup, walaupun.

193
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:04,780
Perempuan gila itu...

194
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:06,740
Kacau betul!

195
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:08,310
Oh, ia membakar saya.

196
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:12,380
Jeneral, mengapa kita tidak melawan jalan keluar

197
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:14,310
dan mati bersama-sama dengan askar Chong?

198
00:10:14,950 --> 00:10:15,990
Lebih banyak saya membunuh,

199
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:16,830
lebih berbaloi.

200
00:10:18,950 --> 00:10:20,470
Belum tiba masanya untuk mati.

201
00:10:21,740 --> 00:10:22,860
Sebelum musuh tiba,

202
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:24,710
saya telah meminta anak buah saya untuk meninjau kawasan ini.

203
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,430
Terdapat laluan rahsia

204
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,140
di sebelah cerah Gunung Peng.

205
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:30,230
Cukup tinggi untuk kuda

206
00:10:31,350 --> 00:10:32,740
dan cukup lebar untuk lima lelaki.

207
00:10:33,590 --> 00:10:34,780
Ia menuju ke belakang musuh.

208
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:37,470
Bak kata orang, tit for tat hanya adil.

209
00:10:38,350 --> 00:10:39,500
Mereka membakar bekalan kami

210
00:10:40,620 --> 00:10:42,310
dan kami akan mengambil bekalan mereka

211
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:43,590
sebagai penghargaan.

212
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:45,900
Jika askar Chong menghantar bekalan,

213
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:47,470
mereka perlu melalui

214
00:10:47,470 --> 00:10:48,540
melalui bandar utara.

215
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:51,380
Saya ada saudara mara di sana juga.

216
00:10:52,110 --> 00:10:53,350
Saya akan menghubungi mereka dengan merpati,

217
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:55,470
meminta mereka melihat kereta gandum.

218
00:10:56,070 --> 00:10:56,910
Kemudian mari kita lakukannya.

219
00:11:18,060 --> 00:11:20,580
(Koleksi Teknik Ketenteraan)

220
00:11:26,430 --> 00:11:27,540
(Duan Xu)
(Kamu palsu.)

221
00:11:28,190 --> 00:11:29,780
(Kamu bukan kerabat empayar.)

222
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:31,350
(Kamu mungkin seorang Chong.)

223
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:34,260
(Mengapa kamu bertempur secara agresif)

224
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:35,100
(untuk Liang Besar)

225
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:36,950
(dan bunuh tentera Chong dengan bersemangat?) [[n]], ada apa sebenarnya dengan kamu) [Xu]] (Duan)

226
00:11:37,140 --> 00:11:38,190
Umum.

227
00:11:38,190 --> 00:11:39,660
Ada apa?

228
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:48,740
Anda mengarahkan saya menyelesaikan

229
00:11:50,430 --> 00:11:51,270
kes kebakaran.

230
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:55,950
Tetapi saya keliru tentang sesuatu.

231
00:11:55,950 --> 00:11:56,900
Saya memohon bimbingan-Mu.

232
00:11:58,500 --> 00:11:59,780
Teruskan.

233
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:01,620
Mengapa anda begitu akrab dengan Chong Utara

234
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:02,860
sedangkan anda tidak pernah menyertai tentera?

235
00:12:03,020 --> 00:12:04,620
Adakah anda mengesyaki

236
00:12:05,260 --> 00:12:07,020
saya ada kaitan dengan mereka?

237
00:12:10,370 --> 00:12:11,230
Ya.

238
00:12:11,230 --> 00:12:12,430
Saya minta awak cari pengintip.

239
00:12:13,350 --> 00:12:14,190
Tetapi anda mengesyaki saya

240
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:21,380
pada mulanya.

241
00:12:22,170 --> 00:12:23,020
Adakah anda bimbang saya bersubahat dengan mereka

242
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,260
dan hanya berpura-pura?

243
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:27,590
Saya tidak pasti.

244
00:12:29,190 --> 00:12:30,110
Tolong jelaskan.

245
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:32,380
Kapten Han, saya dengar

246
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:34,230
awak melarikan diri dari Chong Utara.

247
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:41,540
Anda mesti mempunyai lebih banyak sambungan

248
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:44,540
dengan mereka.

249
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:48,350
Saya tidak ingat apa yang berlaku

